Integration tests
-----------------

If you want to run the integration tests you need an Imagga account with access to all the APIs implemented by the
imagga-java-kit.

1. Add account information to ~/.imagga like this

imagga.key=<YOUR KEY>
imagga.secret=<YOUR SECRET>
imagga.endpoint=<YOUR ENDPOINT>
imagga.connection.timeout=0
imagga.read.timeout=0

2. Run integrations test : imagga-java-kit> mvn -Denv=integration test

